reviewText: It's middle of the road. Yes, it's on a low budget, but the acting is fairly done. It could have been  a lot worse. Kari Wuhrer carries the entire movie, the captain of the ship follows closely. The rest of the actors are just along for the ride.It's always interesting how a hot woman can overcome guys twice her size, get beat up, and not even bruise. ... Only in Hollywood.Anyway, it's a  good watch for a scifi-action flick, even if you just watch (rent) it once.

reviewText: This movie doesn't display any great acting, but it's not expected in a science fiction B-movie. Kari Wuhrer doesn't get naked in movie, but gets to dive in some water and gets her shirt wet. She is trying to save Los Angeles from getting destroyed by sneaking upto bad guy's spaceship and sabotaging it. The lure of the movie for me is it's about a chick who kicks butt. She shoots a gun too.
summary: Not That Great Acting, Not Expected In This Genre
